statements.sql: select * from `designs` order by `created_at` desc limit 8 offset 0
select `d`.`id`, IFNULL(ROUND(AVG(dr.rating), 2), 0) as avg_rating from `designs` as `d` left join `design_reviews` as `dr` on `d`.`id` = `dr`.`design_id` group by `d`.`id`

select `td`.`design_id`, SUM(td.quantity) as sold_quantity from `transaction_designs` as `td` inner join `transactions` as `t` on `td`.`transaction_id` = `t`.`id` where `t`.`transaction_status` = 'Completed' group by `td`.`design_id`
select * from `users` where exists (select * from `designs` where `users`.`id` = `designs`.`seller_id`)
